OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FDrivers in Portsmouth are being warned
OL,7,Fof delays to journeys, ahead of two
OL,8,FM275 closures in the city.
OL,10,FPortsmouth City Council is closing a
OL,11,Fstretch of the motorway this weekend
OL,12,F(15 May) and also again at the end of
OL,13,FMay, to allow for essential
OL,14,Fmaintenance to take place.
OL,16,FThousands of people use the motorway
OL,17,Fevery day, which links the island to
OL,18,Fthe wider motorway network and A27.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
