PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FThe route is somewhat of an
OL,7,Fengineering marvel, with its bridges
OL,8,Frequiring specialist engineering
OL,9,Fexpertise to stay open.
OL,11,FThe two closures will allow engineers
OL,12,Fto 'raise' the bridges up, and replace
OL,13,Fcorroded bridge joints and bearing.
OL,15,FWhen will the M275 closures take place?
OL,17,FPortsmouth City Council and Colas will
OL,18,Fclose the Southbound M275 at the
OL,19,FTipner interchange from 10pm on Friday
OL,20,F15 May until 5am on Monday 18 May.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
