OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FFurther lane restrictions will be in
OL,7,Fplace on other parts of the motorway
OL,8,Fto manage traffic flows.
OL,10,FMotorists will still be able to access
OL,11,Fthe Southbound carriageway from the
OL,12,FM27, but drivers on the A27 will not
OL,13,Fbe able to access the route. They will
OL,14,Fbe diverted onto other local roads.
OL,16,FM275 traffic will be diverted through
OL,17,Fthe Tipner Interchange roundabout
OL,18,Fwhilst the affected bridge is out of
OL,19,Faction.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
