OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FA second closure will take place
OL,7,Fbetween Friday 29 May and Monday 1
OL,8,FJune, this time affecting the
OL,9,Fnorthbound carriageway.
OL,11,FHowever, during this closure access
OL,12,Fwill be maintained to both the M27 and
OL,13,FA27, with traffic once again being
OL,14,Fdiverted through the Tipner
OL,15,FInterchange.
OL,17,FWhat diversions will be in place?
OL,19,FPortsmouth City Council says 'clearly
OL,20,Fsigned diversion routes' throughout
OL,21,Fboth weekends.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
