PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FOther routes, such as Eastern Road,
OL,7,Fare likely to be very busy and some
OL,8,Fdisruption to public transport is
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,FSome bus routes may be diverted, with
OL,12,Fpassengers told to check with their
OL,13,Foperators, such as Stagecoach South or
OL,14,FFirst Solent, before travelling.
OL,16,FThe council suggests drivers consider
OL,17,Falternatives to driving, such as using
OL,18,Fthe Park & Ride, which will remain
OL,19,Fopen during the motorway closures.
OL,21,FWhy is the M275 closing?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
