CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FThe M275 was built in the 1970s over
OL,7,Fmainly reclaimed land. It is a major
OL,8,Ffeat of engineering, with complex
OL,9,Fbridges spanning several stretches of
OL,10,Fthe 2-mile motorway.
OL,12,FIt opened 50 years ago, and has
OL,13,Frequired specialist maintenance ever
OL,14,Fsince.
OL,16,FPortsmouth City Council runs the road,
OL,17,Fand it is one of the few motorways in
OL,18,FEngland to not be maintained by
OL,19,FNational Highways.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FThese closures are needed to replace
OL,7,Fcorroded bridge joints and bearings,
OL,8,Fwhich are reaching the end of their
OL,9,Fusable life.
OL,11,FTo do this, they 'jack' up the whole
OL,12,Fbridge to expose the bearings. The
OL,13,Fcouncil describes it as a bit like
OL,14,Fchanging a wheel on a car.
OL,16,FThe short-term closures will mean the
OL,17,FM275 stays resilient for the future
OL,18,Fand keeps drivers safe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
