OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778847105
OL,3,CM275 closures: What drivers need to
OL,4,Cknow as the route shuts for maintenance
OL,6,FA Portsmouth City Council spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This work forms part of the
OL,8,Fongoing investment in maintaining
OL,9,FPortsmouth's road network and is
OL,10,Fessential to keeping the M275 and its
OL,11,Fstructures safe for future use.
OL,13,F"Carrying out this type of highly
OL,14,Ftechnical work requires specialist
OL,15,Fskills and careful planning. By
OL,16,Fdiverting traffic in one direction at
OL,17,Fa time and scheduling the work at
OL,18,Fweekends, we are aiming to manage the
OL,19,Fimpact as effectively as possible."
